Package: rcol
Title: R Client for the Catalogue of Life / ChecklistBank API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Markus", "Döring", , "mdoering@gbif.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7757-1889")),
    person("Catalogue of Life", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Access the Catalogue of Life (COL) through the ChecklistBank
    (CLB) web API <https://api.checklistbank.org>. Match scientific names
    against any public dataset or the latest COL release, look up datasets,
    taxa and name usages, navigate the taxonomic tree, run the ChecklistBank
    name and value parsers, and discover the latest annual and monthly COL
    base and extended releases. Modelled on the conventions of 'rgbif' and
    'taxadb'.
